title: Loiter Squad Season 3 HDTV 720p
description:
This is the complete third season of Loiter Squad as well as my first upload. Last episode aired last Thursday and I love this show so I thought, why not upload it? I know it can be a pain to download the episodes separate, so I'll put them together for you. If you can seed, that would be great, I'll be seeding forever (unless all my computers break), but the start will be a problem since, right now, I'm not able to seed 24/7 so please be patient.

Info from the first episode:

Video:
1280x720 (16:9) 23.976 fps AVC

Audio:
English 2.0 Stereo AC3 (448 kbps)

(I don't have MediaInfo installed so I got the bitrates from VLC and I didn't get the video bit rates, it's probably in the thousands or so.)

Thanks to the people for uploading all the episodes! Especially in this quality!
